{"tid":1708701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實如果連續一星期黎明行動，係咪應該上午行動，但下午兩點後就休息？","createTime":"2019-11-11T16:08:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T16:58:41.000Z","uid":36494,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"67a773454b8c3d52d7d97731c099e2e525f995cf","tid":1708701,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T16:08:06.000Z","msg":"黎明行動令大家都返唔到，呢樣大家都明<br />\n其實行動持續到下午兩三點，已經可以阻塞到絕大部分返工的人<br />\n<br />\n唔需要搞到黃昏甚至夜晚<br />\n由朝搞到夜，邊有精力去持續阻塞一星期<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">應該連續一星期 <br />\n上午七點至下午三點 行動 <br />\n三點至晚上休息<br />\n先有精力持續行動一星期</span></span>"},{"pid":"8ff960d3fd5670e010aa7a5da3ad36881b26cfd2","tid":1708701,"uid":305579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T16:08:28.000Z","msg":"（有片）警賊PC46283煽動他人犯罪<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1708533\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1708533</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c054fdc7c1064353fa1cc24980e33964d73a1025","tid":1708701,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T16:08:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2e26e01962538083535b298093d94f1adf6cff14","tid":1708701,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T16:08:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b7d847cbb0b4a6850ae1660e26a797610f9ed804","tid":1708701,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T16:09:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e8e1c9da85ace510fb2b554ab7e61c082e018be1","tid":1708701,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T16:09:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c3455ea5611f6535796504ff3637af4572c81f87","tid":1708701,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T16:09:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e895f9b762ce7fe8d183c026a0f610df51ad158d","tid":1708701,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T16:09:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=